--- Security: Secrets & Keys ---

.env
*.pem
*.key
*.vault

--- Project Specific: Metadata & Paths ---

This prevents your forensic and path data from being pushed

/hanger/
data/archive/
data/server_side_data/

# Ignore all actual data payloads
data/ingress/*
data/processed/*
data/vault/*
data/logs/*

# Keep the folders by allowing .gitkeep files
!data/**/.gitkeep

# Ignore actual system secrets
config/system/system_config/vent_master-map.json

--- Python System Files ---

pycache/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.pytest_cache/
.venv
venv/
env/

--- OS Specific Files ---

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db